article_title: On The Last Frontier, a Democrat fights a rising GOP tide
article_text: Control of the U.S. Senate might be decided by a race in which the campaigns fight over snowmobiling skills and where an endorsement from the nominee of a secessionist party who went to federal prison for corruption could help to sway the outcome.
